<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.8 Articles promulgated in full by the order of GIO, Executive Yuan on March 9, 1994. Ref: (83) Chiang-Guang-(1) Tze No. 03761.
2.The amendment of examples listed in Subparagraph 2 in the attached table of Article 3 promulgated by the order of GIO, Executive Yuan on September 20, 1995 Ref: (84)Chiang-Guang-(1) Tze No.15204.
3.7 Articles in full and the name of these standards were amended and promulgated by the order of GIO, Executive Yuan on September 15, 1999 Ref: (88) Chiang-Guang-(1) Tze No.15040. These standards shall come into effect as of the date of promulgation. (original name: The production standards for cable television advertisement)]]></沿革內容>
<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards are promulgated according to Paragraph 2, Article 50 of the Cable Radio and Television Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The cable radio and television advertisements in these standards shall refer to the images, sounds and contents transmitted by the system operators to promote commodities, concepts, services, or images.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The contents of the advertisements shall not
1. Violate compulsory or prohibitive regulations under the law;
2. Impair the physical or mental health of children or juveniles; or
3. Disrupt public order or adversely affect good social customs.
The demonstration of the foregoing section is set as an Attached Table.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The cable radio and television enterprises shall transmit certain advertisements in the time slots and with the encoding method designated by the central regulatory agency.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The transmission of advertizing should be distinguishable by subtitles, picture cards, narration, music or other appropriate means from the transmission of programs.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Stipulations for production and transmission of cable radio and television advertisement shall be promulgated by the central regulatory agency.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 7</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards shall come into effect as of the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
